what is the proper way to potty train a small house dog the proper way to potty train a dog whenever the dog is in the house and not crated put a body harness and leash on the dog tie end of leash to your belt wherever you go the dog goes when you see the dog start to signal sniff circle scratch that it's got to go than run the dog out to where you want it to go praise reward immediately and use a command word consistently when the dog shows it's learned to go outside consistently by dragging you to the outside than you can undo the leash from your belt keep the leash on the dog still and keep an eye on it whenever it is in the house and not crated so if it starts to make an accident you can grab the leash and run it outside once it is going outside with no attempted accidents for at least a week than you can take the leash off the most common mistake in potty training is giving the dog freedom to roam the house without supervision where the human doesn't see the dog signal it needs to go and if your dog is a puppy remember it only has an average hold time of hour for every month of it's life until they reach months or so and can hold overnight usually Dog training Housebreaking Crate training Aerial (dance move) Dog Kitesurfing Ferret Professional wrestling match types Dog agility Dog collar Paranoia Agent Leash Piccolo Junior Saga Fox hunting Nintendogs Basset Hound Beer Hall Putsch Cerberus Constitution of the Turkish Republic of Northern Cyprus Aikido Pakistani cricket team in West Indies in 2005 2005 Iditarod Shetland Sheepdog Socialization 24 Hours of Le Mans Dog show Futurama (TV series - season 5) USS Sea Dog (SS-401) German Shepherd Dog Boy Scouts of America Lady and the Tramp Fancy rat Elimination communication Speaker of the British House of Commons Cat Episodes of Lost (Season 1) Minor characters in Teen Titans (animated series) Alan Arnett McLeod Dobermann Falconry Beethoven (film) The Amber Spyglass Police dog Disgaea: Hour of Darkness Piccolo (Dragon 